txt.en: DNT - 'Why thank you, dear. I am sure this will help those poor spirits find their rest.'
Nan Mabli has asked you to burn incense at barrows in the South Downs.\n\nThe barrows are located at Gond Orchal, in the South Downs.
'Why thank you, dear. I am sure this will help those poor spirits find their rest.'
Something has stirred the bones of the dead within the barrows of the South Downs.
You should let Nan Mabli know that you have burned incense at the barrows.\n\nNan Mabli is at in the South Downs.
DNT - 'I have never seen the spirits this restless. I do so hope we can help them find peace.'
'I have never seen the spirits this restless. I do so hope we can help them find peace.'

'Oh hello, young [placeholder]. I am Mabli, though most call me Nan Mabli. I wonder if you could help me. Every year around this time, we have a tradition in my family to come and burn incense at the tombs to appease the spirits within. However, this year the spirits are quite incensed already!\n\n'I am no match for their wrath, but perhaps someone of your capabilities might go where an old woman cannot. Would you burn the incense for me at their tombs?'
